        public NoRecipientFoundException(String message,

        Creates an exception with a specified message and optional reason varargs. Usually the vendor ID followed by the message type ID and if exclusive delivery was used the recipient ID should be provided as reasons.

        public NoRecipientFoundException(String message,
                         Throwable exception,
                         Object... reasons)
        Creates an exception with a specified message and optional reason varargs based on an existing exception. Usually the vendor ID followed by the message type ID and if exclusive delivery was used the recipient ID should be provided as reasons.
        Parameters:
        message - the specified exception message
        exception - the existing exception, which has to be encapsulated
        reasons - the optional reasons, which let to the exception
